name: Rdio+GoogleGlass
body:
### Rdio+GoogleGlass by Gino Corrales
Rdio application running within Google Glass. Started as a HackIllinois hack and will be developed more in depth.

### Welcome to Rdio+GoogleGlass.
This is the front end of Rdio+GoogleGlass App. Find more info @ https://github.com/ginocorrales/GGlassRdio

### Support my Project
If you like the idea of this app, send me an email to gino.p.corrales@gmail.com or visit my [website](http://ginopcorrales.com). Follow me @ginocorrales.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
